    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An order containing six families, over 300 genera, and over 3,300 species of ray-finned fish including the carp, minnows, loaches, and their relatives.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
